Description
-----------
A Single page application based on React frameworks.
The application is built from React's functional components so that React Hooks can be utilised rather than class-based components to handle states.

Technology used :
* JavaScript.
* JSX.
* Functional React Components.
* uniqid Package.
* event listeners
* Desctructuring 
* Context variables

Hooks used :
* useState
* create / useContext
